<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l5">wır ewr <expan>VVeıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . Daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſıch </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Johanſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l6">Ret ein gütlıch ſteen . <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Eker vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> beſtellt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l7">bıs auf ſand Barthlomeuſtag ſchıerıſt . Vnd in dem <expan>gütlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l8">ſteen . für <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> vıcʒtum vnd dıe Ret ʒu </ab>
