<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l12">tag <expan>leıhe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet . dıe bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> da ſey vnd </ab>
