</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_210" id="105r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Kelheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> als wir ewch vormals auch
              <expan>verschribe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sprüch
                <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die Weinmar Eker zu uns maint zu
              <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, lassen wir ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Johans<ex>en,</ex></expan> ret ein gütlich steen <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Eker und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> bestellt
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bis auf <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Barthlomeustag schierist</q>24.08.1415</note>
</app> und in dem <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> steen für
              <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>ans</ex></expan> vicztum und die ret zu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag
            zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> gen Strawbing auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">samstag am achttentag vor sand Bartholmeustag
                nehst</q>17.08.1415</note>
</app>, <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> daz ir uns ewr erber
              <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> rat auf
                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> tag <expan>leihe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                <expan>send<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, die bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> da sey und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> glimpf und
            unglimpf <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan>; und getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> wol, daz ir uns des niht
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czeihet</expan>. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Larencii. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Der stat zu Tekendorff <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>. </ab>
</div>
